# Agent source index

Read sources in this priority order when resolving intent vs implementation:

1. **Code** — ground truth for what runs today
2. **v2 init spec** — `DevSpecs/hftr-v2.init.spec.md` (read-only)
3. **v1 snapshot** — `agent-docs/research/v1-reference/` + `packages/db/src/seed/catalogs/`
   (vendored into this repo; the external v1 workspace is historical only — never a dependency)
4. **agent-docs/** — living truth; must stay synced with code
5. **User chat** — implementation decisions → log in `dev-intent/decisions-log.md`

