## Cursor workspace

Skills/workflows: `.cursor/README.md`. Invoke `session-start` at task start.
Credentials/secrets work: invoke `secrets-hygiene` skill + rule
`.cursor/rules/secrets-hygiene.mdc` (D-027, D-074).
Close every implementation run: **verify → curate → invoke `commit-message` skill**
(`.cursor/workflows/end-of-run.md` or `/end-run`). Per-file commit bodies required.
